quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  35,1,"Kurumbidzwa nekutenda kwose ndekwaAllah, Musiki wematenga nenyika, vakaita ngirozi vatumwa vane mapapiro maviri, matatu kana mana. Vanowedzera mukusika zvavanoda. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanokwanisa kuita zvose"
  35,2,"Kubva mutsitsi Allah dzavanopa kuvanhu, hapana angazvidzivirira; uye dzavanodzivirira hapana angape mushure mezvo. Uye ndivo samasimba, vane hungwaru hwose"
  35,3,Imi vanhu! Rangarirai makomborero aAllah kwamuri! Pane here mumwe musiki kunze kwaAllah avo vanokupai kubva kudenga (mvura) uye nepasi? Laa ilaaha illaa Huwa (Hakuna umwe ane kodzero yekunamatwa kunze kwavo). Saka munotendeukirei (kubva kwavari)
  35,4,"Uye vakakuramba (Muhammad (SAW)), zvirokwazvo vamwe vatume vakarambwa mushure mako. Uye kuna Allah ndiko kunodzoserwa nyaya dzose"
  35,5,"Imi vanhu! Zvirokwazvo, vimbiso yaAllah ndeyechokwadi. Saka musarega hupenyu huno huchikunyengedzai, uye mambo wevanyengedzi (satani) asakunyengedzei nezvaAllah"
  35,6,"Zvirokwazvo, Satani imhandu kwamuri, saka mutorei semuvengi. Anoshevedza vateveri vake kuti vave vagari vemumariri emoto"
  35,7,"Avo vasingatendi, chavo uchange uri mutongo wakaomarara; uye avo vanotenda (muhumwechete hwaAllah) zvekare voita mabasa akanaka, vachawana ruregerero uye nemubairo mukuru (Paradhiso)"